                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">WhatsApp 最新推出了 iOS 平台上的更新，WhatsApp 版本 24.14.81 增長了動態影片和音訊的長度至 60 秒，新添了設定上傳相片和影片畫質的功能，並更新了 WhatsApp 的通話介面。</p><figure id="attachment_1250843" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1250843" style="width: 268px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-1250843 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1757-268x580.jpeg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1757-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1757.jpeg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1250843" class="wp-caption-text"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;">▲WhatsApp 24.14.81 版本記錄</span></figcaption></figure><h2>動態</h2><figure id="attachment_1250844" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1250844" style="width: 268px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-1250844 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1759-268x580.jpeg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1759-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1759.jpeg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1250844" class="wp-caption-text"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;">▲動態影片和音訊的長度至 60 秒</span></figcaption></figure><h2>可設定相片/影片的上傳畫質</h2><figure id="attachment_1250845" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1250845" style="width: 268px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-1250845 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1760-268x580.jpeg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1760-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1760.jpeg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1250845" class="wp-caption-text"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;">▲在設定中進入「儲存空間及數據」</span></figcaption></figure><figure id="attachment_1250846" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1250846" style="width: 268px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-1250846 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1761-268x580.jpeg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1761-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1761.jpeg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1250846" class="wp-caption-text"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;">▲可設定媒體上載畫質</span></figcaption></figure><figure id="attachment_1250847" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1250847" style="width: 268px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-1250847 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1762-268x580.jpeg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1762-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1762.jpeg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1250847" class="wp-caption-text"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;">▲有普通的標準畫質和高清畫質選擇</span></figcaption></figure><h2>新通話介面</h2><figure id="attachment_1250852" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1250852" style="width: 694px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-1250852 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/whatsapp_new_interfa-694x386.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="386" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/whatsapp_new_interfa-694x386.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/whatsapp_new_interfa.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1250852" class="wp-caption-text"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;">▲舊版本 WhatsApp 通話介面為上拉式</span></figcaption></figure><p style="text-align: center;">圖片來源：<a href="https://indianexpress.com/article/technology/social/whatsapp-starts-rolling-out-new-interface-for-voice-video-calls-on-ios-7416623/">The Indian Express</a></p><figure id="attachment_1250841" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1250841" style="width: 268px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-1250841 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1755-268x580.jpeg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1755-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1755.jpeg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1250841" class="wp-caption-text"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;">▲新通話介面變成五按鈕設計</span></figcaption></figure><figure id="attachment_1250842" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1250842" style="width: 268px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-1250842 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1756-268x580.jpeg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1756-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1756.jpeg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1250842" class="wp-caption-text"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;">▲最左的選項按鈕</span></figcaption></figure><p>更新後的通話介面取消了以往的上拉式選單而轉成五按鈕設計，以選項按鈕取代了上拉式選單。</p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/11/samsung-galaxy-ai-4/ai/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Galaxy AI 或將擴展至第三方應用程式     WhatsApp 或有實時翻譯功能</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/30/create-ai-powered-images-within-whatsapp-chats/ai/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">WhatsApp 將加入 Meta AI   用戶可人工智能生成圖像</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/29/wfsfaa-scam/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">被冒認發出虛假 WhatsApp 訊息　職學處澄清並呼籲市民提防</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/17/whatsapp-update-24-14-81/software/iphone-app/">WhatsApp 更新 iOS 介面　動態影片長度達 60 秒 + 預設相片上傳畫質</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
